NK010(tha)009:0: phur pa rgyud lugs las tshe sgrub nyi zla'i za ma tog ces bya ba bzhugs so //
NK010(tha)009:1: gzhom bral rdo rje'i ngo bo nyid //
NK010(tha)009:2: bgres rgud spangs pa'i gzhon nu'i skur //
NK010(tha)009:3: yongs grub dpal chen tshe yi lhar //
NK010(tha)009:4: nges pa rnyed pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK010(tha)009:5: 'dir rdo rje khros pa'i bshad rgyud le'u brgyad pa
NK010(tha)009:6: las tshe'i rig 'dzin bsgrub pa'i don gtan la dbab
NK010(tha)009:11: tshe'i rnam dbye bstan pa dang /
NK010(tha)009:15: tshe ni rnam pa gsum yin te //
NK010(tha)009:17: nyams shing 'pho ba thig le'i tshe //
NK010(tha)009:18: 'khrul zhing rtog pa snang ba'i tshe //
NK010(tha)009:20: dang po ni chos nyid kyi bden pa mngon sum
NK010(tha)009:21: du mthong ba rnams la skye 'chi rang mtshan pa
NK010(tha)009:22: ma grub ste / bde chen lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes kyi chos nyid ni kun rdzob dang /
NK010(tha)009:24: 'phags pas rga dang na ba dang //
NK010(tha)009:25: 'chi ba'i sdug bsngal rtsad nas spangs //
NK010(tha)009:28: rnam smin gyi lus rten 'di dang por yang khams thig le'i 'du 'phrod pa brten nas chags /
NK010(tha)009:29: bar du yang bla tshe srog gsum de la brten /
NK010(tha)009:30: tha mar yang khams de rgud cing 'pho ba las lus rten 'jig pa'i phyir ro //
NK010(tha)009:32: 'tsho ba'i rnam par rtog pa la shin tu'ang bden
NK010(tha)009:33: 'dzin gyi blo dang bcas pas so so skye bo
NK010(tha)009:34: rnams la skye 'chi rang rgyud par 'char ba la
NK010(tha)009:35: 'khrul zhing rtog pa'i tshe zhes nges pa can du
NK010(tha)009:36: brjod pa'o // de las 'dir tshe bsgrub pa'i ngo
NK010(tha)009:37: bo ni nyams shing 'pho bar byed pa'i thig le'i
NK010(tha)009:38: tshe 'phel zhing brtan pa'i thabs sgrub pa yin na
NK010(tha)009:39: brjod pa'o // / de'i sngon du nyams pa'i rgyu ngos bzung nas spang bar bya ste /
NK010(tha)009:40: nyams pa'i rgyu ni 'di lta ste //
NK010(tha)009:41: dam nyams bzhin 'gyur spyod lam nyams //
NK010(tha)009:43: zhe sdang rgyas dang bgegs dang phrad //
NK010(tha)009:44: bred sngangs rbod gtong khar rbad dang //
NK010(tha)009:45: dam can gtor chag tshe nyams 'gyur //
NK010(tha)009:48: bla ma la gus rgyud la sbyangs //
NK010(tha)009:50: dam can nye bar 'gyur pa yin //
NK010(tha)009:54: rdo rje theg pa'i lam thabs kyi che bas bskyed
NK010(tha)009:55: rdzogs kyi lam gnyis ka nas tshe sgrub pa'i man
NK010(tha)009:56: ngag khyad par can yod pa las /
NK010(tha)009:57: 'dir dang po'i phyogs ltar ston pa la /
NK010(tha)009:58: nyams pa gso bar 'dod pa yis //
NK010(tha)009:59: bkra shis sa la man+dala bya //
NK010(tha)009:61: lha yi rten ni mar me dgu //
NK010(tha)009:62: khro bcu'i phur pas bgegs bsal zhing //
NK010(tha)009:63: bdud rtsi lnga dang sman lnga dang //
NK010(tha)009:64: phur pa brten pa'i zas mchog la //
NK010(tha)009:65: thod pa lcags dang rin chen snod //
NK010(tha)009:66: bum pa yid 'ong mdzes pa ru //
NK010(tha)009:67: bsgrubs pas tshe ni rab tu 'phel //
NK010(tha)009:68: zhes pas bkra shis pa'i sa la stegs bu byas
NK010(tha)009:69: pa'i steng man+dala pad+ma 'dab bzhi re kh+aa can la
NK010(tha)009:70: rigs lnga'i phyag mtshan phyogs ma 'chol ba bris pa'i
NK010(tha)009:71: dbus su rdo rje rgya gram gyi steng bum pa
NK010(tha)009:72: bcud ldan / de'i mtha' skor du mar me dgu /
NK010(tha)009:73: ra ba'i phyi skor la khro bcu'i phur pa /
NK010(tha)009:74: de'i nang khol du tshe'i 'brang rgyas sam /
NK010(tha)009:75: tshe ril gyi rtse mo tsan dan nam /
NK010(tha)009:76: bkra shis pa'i shing gi phur bu dbal gru bzhi pa dar snas brgyan pa gzug /
NK010(tha)009:78: lcang lo'i thod pa kha sbyar du //
NK010(tha)009:79: bdud rtsi'i rtsa ba lnga bstsal nas //
NK010(tha)009:80: rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba'i ril bu gzhug /
NK010(tha)009:81: de bzhin bza' ba bca' ba dang //
NK010(tha)009:82: btung dang bldag dang gzhib la sogs //
NK010(tha)009:83: zhes pa ltar thod chang sman phud kyis bran pa dang /
NK010(tha)009:84: mchod gtor nyer spyod la sogs pa tshang bar bsag go //
NK010(tha)009:86: dang po las gzhung bsrang ba ni /
NK010(tha)009:87: bdag mdun 'jug pa gcig gi ngang nas lha'i rnal 'byor bsgoms la dzapa kha phye nas /
NK010(tha)009:89: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hoh+aa yur+dz+ny+aa
NK010(tha)009:90: na +aa kar+sha ya dzah ru lu ru lu h+aum
NK010(tha)009:96: b+h+r+aum badz+ra +aa yu she h+aum a /
NK010(tha)009:98: thun mtshams su tshe 'gugs bya ba ni /
NK010(tha)009:99: gegs kyis tshe rnams mi ster na //
NK010(tha)009:100: tshe dpag med kyang khro bo ste //
NK010(tha)009:101: phyogs bcu nam mkha'i khams bkang nas //
NK010(tha)009:102: sgra skad drag po bton nas ni //
NK010(tha)009:103: thams cad ma lus gdul bar bya //
NK010(tha)009:104: zhes pa'i dmigs pa dang bcas /
NK010(tha)009:106: dbus nas rang byung grub pa'i lha //
NK010(tha)009:107: dpal chen rdo rje khrag 'thung dang //
NK010(tha)009:108: khro mo rdo rje dbyings phyug ma //
NK010(tha)009:109: mthing nag mi 'gyur nam mkha'i mdog /
NK010(tha)009:110: zhal gcig phyag gnyis khro bo'i tshul //
NK010(tha)009:111: rdo rjes gdug pa 'dul mdzad cing //
NK010(tha)009:112: bee d+aur+ya yi bum pa g.yon //
NK010(tha)009:113: nang na 'chi med bdud rtsis bkang //
NK010(tha)009:114: ka shi dar gyi mgul chings la //
NK010(tha)009:115: dpag bsam ljon pas kha brgyan nas //
NK010(tha)009:116: yab yum bde ba'i sbyor ba las //
NK010(tha)009:118: rdo rje khrag 'thung dpag med kyis //
NK010(tha)009:119: stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten bkang //
NK010(tha)009:120: zhal nas tshe yi sngags zlos shing //
NK010(tha)009:121: lha klu gnod sbyin gshin rje dang //
NK010(tha)009:122: mkha' 'gro'i lag nas tshe khug cig /
NK010(tha)009:123: drongs shig drongs shig tshe drongs shig /
NK010(tha)009:124: tshe bum 'di la byin gyis rlobs //
NK010(tha)009:125: tshe bum 'di la rtags phyung zhig /
NK010(tha)009:126: rig 'dzin sgrub po'i tshe spel cig /
NK010(tha)009:127: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)009:128: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK010(tha)009:131: shar lho nub byang phyogs bzhi nas //
NK010(tha)009:132: rigs bzhi'i khrag 'thung yum dang bcas //
NK010(tha)009:133: rang rang rigs kyi sku mdog can //
NK010(tha)009:134: g.yas pa rang rtags g.yon pa na //
NK010(tha)009:135: shel gser pad+ma r+aa ga dang //
NK010(tha)009:136: in+d+ra n+ai la'i bum pa bsnams //
NK010(tha)009:137: nang na 'chi med bdud rtsis bkang //
NK010(tha)009:138: ka shi'i dar gyi mgul chings la //
NK010(tha)009:139: dpag bsam ljon pas kha brgyan nas //
NK010(tha)009:140: yab yum bde ba'i sbyor ba las //
NK010(tha)009:142: rigs bzhi'i khrag 'thung dpag med kyis //
NK010(tha)009:143: stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten rten bkang //
NK010(tha)009:144: zhal nas tshe yi sngags zlos shing //
NK010(tha)009:145: lha klu gnod sbyin gshin rje dang //
NK010(tha)009:146: mkha' 'gro'i lag nas tshe khug cig /
NK010(tha)009:147: drongs shig drongs shig tshe drongs shig /
NK010(tha)009:148: tshe bum 'di la byin gyis rlobs //
NK010(tha)009:149: tshe bum 'di la rtags phyung zhig /
NK010(tha)009:150: rig 'dzin sgrub po'i tshe spel cig /
NK010(tha)009:151: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)009:152: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK010(tha)009:155: dbus nas rang byung grub pa'i lha //
NK010(tha)009:156: dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu ni //
NK010(tha)009:157: zhal gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi bgrad //
NK010(tha)009:158: gar dgu'i rol pas gnas mdzad cing //
NK010(tha)009:160: yab yum gnyis med sbyor ba'i sgras //
NK010(tha)009:161: dus gsum bud+d+ha rab mchod nas //
NK010(tha)009:162: byang chub sems kyi thig le ni //
NK010(tha)009:163: mu tig khu 'phang dbab tu gsol //
NK010(tha)009:164: tshe bum 'di la byin gyis rlobs //
NK010(tha)009:165: tshe bum 'di la rtags phyung zhig /
NK010(tha)009:166: rig 'dzin sgrub po'i tshe spel cig /
NK010(tha)009:167: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)009:168: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dza h+aum bam hoh
NK010(tha)009:169: +aa yur+dz+ny+aa na a kar+sha ya dzah ru lu ru
NK010(tha)009:172: sgrol yum e ka dza ti ma //
NK010(tha)009:173: chos kyi dbyings kyi mkha' 'gro yum //
NK010(tha)009:174: khrag 'thung lha tshogs mnyes byed ma //
NK010(tha)009:175: bud+d+ha kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK010(tha)009:176: bde 'od nyi ma'i gzi brjid kyis //
NK010(tha)009:177: mkha' 'gro thams cad dbang bsdus nas //
NK010(tha)009:178: byang chub sems kyi thig le ni //
NK010(tha)009:179: mu tig khu 'phang dbab tu gsol //
NK010(tha)009:180: tshe bum 'di la byin gyis rlobs //
NK010(tha)009:181: tshe bum 'di la rtags phyung zhig /
NK010(tha)009:182: rig 'dzin sgrub po'i tshe spel cig /
NK010(tha)009:183: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)009:184: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK010(tha)009:186: koo r+ai la sogs ma mo brgyad //
NK010(tha)009:187: seng ha la sogs phra men brgyad //
NK010(tha)009:188: sras mchog rigs lnga yum dang bcas //
NK010(tha)009:189: khro bcu khra phyag sgo ma rnams //
NK010(tha)009:190: gegs chen 'dul zhing khro tshul ston //
NK010(tha)009:191: g.yas na lcags kyu phur pa bsnams //
NK010(tha)009:192: g.yon na bdud rtsi'i bum pa bsnams //
NK010(tha)009:193: thugs ka nyi zla kha sbyor nas //
NK010(tha)009:194: tshe 'dzin thugs kyi dpal be'u nas //
NK010(tha)009:196: khug cig khug cig tshe khug cig /
NK010(tha)009:197: drongs shig drongs shig tshe drongs shig /
NK010(tha)009:198: phyogs skyong lag nas tshe drongs shig /
NK010(tha)009:199: tshe bum 'di la byin gyis rlobs //
NK010(tha)009:200: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK010(tha)009:206: khrag 'thung rigs lnga'i thugs kar sba //
NK010(tha)009:207: mi 'gyur tshe yi thig le la //
NK010(tha)009:208: rdo rjes rgyas gdab mi shigs dbus //
NK010(tha)009:210: rin chen rgyas gdab bsam bzhin 'grub //
NK010(tha)009:211: pad+mas rgyas gdab nyon mongs bral //
NK010(tha)009:212: rgya gram rgyas gdab don rnams 'grub //
NK010(tha)009:213: ye shes lnga yi rgyas gdab pas //
NK010(tha)009:214: dbyings kyi thig ler mi shigs shog /
NK010(tha)009:216: zhes chos nyid kyi ngang du tshe sba'o //
NK010(tha)009:219: khol ba tshe yi rtags yin no //
NK010(tha)009:221: gsum pa rjes la dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK010(tha)009:222: bsgrub pa thon pa'i dus tshogs gtor bzang po bya /
NK010(tha)009:223: dam tshig nyams chag dag par byas la /
NK010(tha)009:224: dkyil 'khor gyi mar me rnams sbar /
NK010(tha)009:226: dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu ni //
NK010(tha)009:227: bde chen rgyas pa'i b+ha ga'i dbyings //
NK010(tha)009:229: 'gyur ba med pa tshe yi thugs //
NK010(tha)009:230: thabs kyi spyod pas 'gro don du //
NK010(tha)009:231: byams dang snying rjes gang 'dul ba //
NK010(tha)009:232: sangs rgyas phrin las rdzogs mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)009:233: dbang dang byin rlabs bdag stsol cig /
NK010(tha)009:234: zhes pas snyan gsan dbab la bum pa spyi bo'i gnas lngar 'jog cing /
NK010(tha)009:236: khrag 'thung lnga yi dbang bskur bas //
NK010(tha)009:237: nyon mongs dug lnga rab dag nas //
NK010(tha)009:238: ye shes lnga rdzogs thig le rgyas //
NK010(tha)009:240: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hoh badz+ra
NK010(tha)009:241: sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro ti shwa r+ai s+t+wam
NK010(tha)009:243: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK010(tha)009:245: ran+ta sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK010(tha)009:247: pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK010(tha)009:249: karma sh+r+ai he ru ka karma kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK010(tha)009:252: zhes bum chu btung zhing nye reg bya /
NK010(tha)009:253: de nas tshe'i dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK010(tha)009:254: bsgrub rdzas rnams phyogs gcig tu byas la /
NK010(tha)009:256: bcom ldan 'das ni khro rgyal gtso //
NK010(tha)009:257: rdo rje srin po'i nam ni langs lags na //
NK010(tha)009:258: gza' skar rgyal po nyi ma rtse shar gyis //
NK010(tha)009:259: bzlas brjod bsnyen pa'i grangs ni them lags na //
NK010(tha)009:260: grub pa'i rtags ni myur du bstan nas kyang //
NK010(tha)009:261: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsal re ran //
NK010(tha)009:262: dbang dang byin rlabs thams cad bdag gsol cig /
NK010(tha)009:264: brjod med spros bral chos kyi sku //
NK010(tha)009:265: sku gsum rdzogs pa khro rgyal sku //
NK010(tha)009:266: mi gnas ye shes nam mkha'i thugs //
NK010(tha)009:267: thun mong ma yin khyad par 'phags //
NK010(tha)009:268: ye shes mi 'gyur dpal be'u nas //
NK010(tha)009:269: bde chen theg le byang chub sems //
NK010(tha)009:270: bdud 'dul rdo rje gzhon nu yi //
NK010(tha)009:271: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub rnams //
NK010(tha)009:272: ma thogs myur du stsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)009:273: mi 'chi tshe yi dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)009:274: mngon par shes pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)009:275: rdzu 'phrul mthu yi dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)009:276: rig pa 'dzin pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)009:277: phrin las rnam bzhi'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)009:278: rigs rgyud 'phel ba'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)009:279: grub mchog brgyad kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)009:280: nad gegs 'joms pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)009:281: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)009:282: zag med bde ba'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)009:283: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dza h+aum bam hoh a mri ta sid+d+hi h+aum h+r+aish+tha /
NK010(tha)009:284: a be sha ya hoh a la la hoh zhes
NK010(tha)009:285: brjod cing dngos grub kyi rdzas la longs spyod do
NK010(tha)009:287: tshe yi dngos grub blang ba yis //
NK010(tha)009:288: nad dang bral zhing sdug bsngal zhi //
NK010(tha)009:289: gegs med nyi zla'i tshe dang mnyam //
